user.intro:
Father of two daughters, a 10 year old and 7 year old.

General Animal Lover.  We have a 1.5 year old Japanese Spitz, a 13 year old Cat, a 3 year old Cockatiel and two 2 year old Chickens.  

Despite living in the suburbs of Fremont in the Bay Area, I feel like I live on a Farm!
